[director] Cut! Say the line
faster. Okay? Faster this time.

89
00:06:18.980 --> 00:06:21.258
[rushed] He said his vision
was blurry. which could suggest...

90
00:06:21.282 --> 00:06:23.718
Cut! Jesus. I think
we gotta fire this guy.

91
00:06:23.851 --> 00:06:25.987
Can we get
somebody else in here?

92
00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:29.123
["Have You Ever
Seen the Rain?" playing]

93
