<i>Shining down like water</i> ♪

96
00:06:56.017 --> 00:07:02.256
♪ <i>I wanna know</i>
<i>Have you ever seen the rain?</i> ♪

97
00:07:04.025 --> 00:07:10.164
♪ <i>I wanna know</i>
<i>Have you ever seen the rain?</i> ♪

98
00:07:10.298 --> 00:07:14.135
<i>Griff. it's Doug. I just ran into
