108
00:07:35.589 --> 00:07:39.961
Look. I get that this is not what you
dreamed about when you were a kid.

109
00:07:40.094 --> 00:07:42.163
But dreams. they go. Huh?

110
00:07:42.296 --> 00:07:44.165
