111
00:07:44.298 --> 00:07:48.302
And. Doug. it is only a matter
of time before all this is yours.

112
00:07:48.436 --> 00:07:49.436
Really?
Yeah.

113
00:07:49.469 --> 00:07:51.839
Look around. Take it all in.

114
00:07:52.873 --> 00:07:54.241
And imagine.

115
00:07:55.943 --> 00:07:58.846
If you do it right. it's a pretty
sweet setup we got here.

116
00:07:58.980 --> 00:08:02.683
This is a B. and maybe even
a B+ life we're talking about.

117
00:08:04.719 --> 00:08:06.287
Hmm.

118
00:08:06.420 --> 00:08:07.965
[spouse] Are you sure
you don't wanna do anything

119
