129
00:08:29.844 --> 00:08:32.380
Who drowns?
Jesus Christ. Doug.

130
00:08:32.513 --> 00:08:34.758
I don't know. Let's just take
a gummy and go to bed early.

131
00:08:34.782 --> 00:08:36.484
Surprise!

132
00:08:36.617 --> 00:08:38.085
