Oh. my God.

158
00:09:30.505 --> 00:09:32.039
It's been too long. pal.

159
00:09:32.173 --> 00:09:34.017
It's so good to see you.
It has been way too long.

160
00:09:34.041 --> 00:09:35.041
Happy birthday.

161
00:09:35.109 --> 00:09:36.710
Thank you for coming out here.

162
00:09:36.844 --> 00:09:38.284
Think I'm gonna
miss this? Never. Oh.

163
00:09:38.345 --> 00:09:40.147
We got a lot
of catching up to do.

164
00:09:40.281 --> 00:09:45.653
Many years ago. a group of young.
passionate artists had a vision.

165
00:09:45.786 --> 00:09:51.425
It was a vision that's not particularly
original or even. uh. good...

166
00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:53.461
[guests chuckle]
but it was theirs.

167
00:09:53.594 --> 00:09:56.831
And so they made
that vision a reality.

168
00:09:56.964 --> 00:09:59.500
And. without further ado.

169
00:09:59.633 --> 00:10:04.638
I present to you
a completely unrestored print

170
00:10:04.772 --> 00:10:09.743
